the evils in their past.  The US has.  Germany has.  Turkey has not.  I
think the Turkish *people* are ready to do so.  It is their leaders acting
like petulant children who cannot.

We should allow their threatened removal of support for Israel or the US to
be a factor.  That would be like Germany insisting that we must agree there
was no Holocaust as a condition of their support.  Phrased like that, I
would assume any ratioanl person would make the right decision.  It's only
because it's so long ago and seems so alien (Turks and Armenians) to so many
people that it's even open to debate.
